  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When using a blood art, blood control, or a (quicken) or (still) ability, you may spend an additional spell point to affect an additional 1 creature per 2 caster levels (minimum 1) at the same time. Each target must be within range and must be affected by the same effect. For a casting that initiates blood control, this additional cost is only incurred once; it is not paid a second time for the free (quicken) or (still) ability. Once created, each blood control is considered a separate sphere effect.</p>\n",
